/>\n但唔知佢用呢樣野逼員工簽有冇法律上既問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"總之唔好貿然簽<br />\n正常都要比幾日時間人地諮詢法律意見啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:37:57.000Z","msg":"抗疫期間，僱主想八折出糧可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n任何更改僱員待遇的要求，例如減薪、更改工作時間、減福利等，都必需要得到僱員同意。如果僱主無視僱員的反對，強行更改僱傭合約重要條款，<span style=\"color: red;\">僱員可以行使「單方面更改僱傭合約引致變相解僱」的權利</span>，向僱主追討一切法定賠償，包括代通知金、遣散費或長期服務金等。<br />\n<br />\n因此，坊間僱主有說法指「不同意減薪，就當自己辭職」，絕對是Bull Shit, 絕對是違反僱傭條例，各位打工仔切勿中計，切勿簽署任何同意書，保障自己的權益，並且盡快聯同同事，諮詢工會求助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/80%25offwage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2F80%2525offwage&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=ba7998a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/80%25offwage</a>"},{"pid":"e360c72a693682102f6f263edf15f970f5ab5cc6","tid":1907993,"uid":59865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e24ec597ad06b7fd5842839f4ac3f2cf875fde2","tid":1907993,"uid":173300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e83f13ebec0bbd60130521837a3dd1f9fa82dd","tid":1907993,"uid":59865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5166a74650ecebcd20f4e90e7cd6fad744c73a89","tid":1907993,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"係囉. 千其唔自己辭. 迫佢炒<br />\n起碼拎返通知金先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"以我理解<br />\n唔簽扣糧張野，佢地會照勞工一個月通知咁解約。<br />\n果個月你照做咁多野照返咁多日工，唔會賠錢即炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620ac3c5fdaa5c47e57a9b28e051f41b8947288b","tid":1907993,"uid":173300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2168569416da48470